Multilingual Sentiment Dataset from Kaggle
Languages: Mixed (French, German, Spanish, etc.)


## Dataset

The dataset used for this project includes multilingual text samples labeled for sentiment classification (positive, negative, neutral).

- Languages: English, French, German, Spanish
- Format: CSV with three columns – `text`, `language`, and `label`

### Sample Format

| text              | language | label    |
|-------------------|----------|----------|
| Je suis très content | fr       | positive |
| Das war schlecht     | de       | negative |
| This is okay         | en       | neutral  |

### Source

Kaggle: 
Link: https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/rtatman/multilingual-twitter-sentiment
